          <td colspan="2" valign="top" class="titulo2">From <em>Wildwood</em>, a novel-in-progress <span class="texto2">by <a href="../../issue5/tanyo_ravicz/bio.php" class="link3">Tanyo Ravicz</a></span></td>
          <td>&nbsp;</td>
